#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:33
msgid ":index:`Advanced Variables <variables; advanced>`"
msgstr ":index:`Extra variabelen <variabelen; extra>`"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:35
msgid ""
"You can make additional tags available by enabling the :doc:`Use track "
"relationships <../config/options_metadata>` and/or the :doc:`Use release "
"relationships <../config/options_metadata>` settings in Picard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:38
msgid ""
"Some variables provide the :index:`MusicBrainz Identifier (MBID) "
"<identifier; musicbrainz, mbid>` of the entity. The MBID is a 32-character "
"identifier assigned to an entity (e.g.: artist, album, track or work) to "
"uniquely identify the entity. For more information about MBIDs, please see "
"the `MusicBrainz Identifier <https://musicbrainz.org/doc/"
"MusicBrainz_Identifier>`_ page in the MusicBrainz documentation."
msgstr ""
"Sommige variabelen bevatten de :index:`MusicBrainz-identificatiecode (MBID) "
"<identificatiecode; musicbrainz, mbid>` van het object. Een MBID is een "
"identificatiecode van 32 tekens die aan een object (zoals een artiest, "
"uitgave, nummer of compositie) is toegewezen om dat object eenduidig te "
"identificeren. Meer informatie over MBID’s kan je vinden op de pagina "
"`MusicBrainz-identificatiecode <https://musicbrainz.org/doc/"
"MusicBrainz_Identifier>`_ in de documentatie van MusicBrainz."

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:42
msgid ""
"Variables will not be created if there was no value retrieved for the "
"variable from the MusicBrainz database."
msgstr ""
"Als er geen waarde uit de databank van MusicBrainz wordt opgehaald, wordt er "
"ook geen variabele voor gemaakt."

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:46
msgid "Release Relationship Variables"
msgstr "Variabelen van uitgaverelaties"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:48
msgid ""
"If you enable tagging with :doc:`Use release relationships <../config/"
"options_metadata>`, you get these extra variables:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:50
msgid "**_release_series**"
msgstr "**_release_series**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:52
msgid ""
"A multi-value variable containing the series titles associated with the "
"release. (*since Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Een meervoudige variabele met de namen van de series die aan de uitgave zijn "
"gekoppeld. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:54
msgid "**_release_seriesid**"
msgstr "**_release_seriesid**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:56
msgid ""
"A multi-value variable containing the series MBIDs associated with the "
"release. (*since Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Een meervoudige variabele met de MBID’s van de series die aan de uitgave "
"zijn gekoppeld. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:58
msgid "**_release_seriescomment**"
msgstr "**_release_seriescomment**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:60
msgid ""
"A multi-value variable containing the series disambiguation comments "
"associated with the release. (*since Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Een meervoudige variabele met de verduidelijkingen van de series die aan de "
"uitgave zijn gekoppeld. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:62
msgid "**_release_seriesnumber**"
msgstr "**_release_seriesnumber**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:64
msgid ""
"If the release is part of one of more series, this multi-value variable "
"contains the positions (numbers) of the release in those series. (*since "
"Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Als de uitgave deel van een of meer series uitmaakt, bevat deze meervoudige "
"variabele de posities (nummers) van de uitgave in die serie of series. "
"(*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:66
msgid "**_releasegroup_series**"
msgstr "**_releasegroup_series**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:68
msgid ""
"A multi-value variable containing the series titles associated with the "
