msgstr ""
"Een meervoudige variabele met de namen van de series die aan de uitgavegroep "
"zijn gekoppeld. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:70
msgid "**_releasegroup_seriesid**"
msgstr "**_releasegroup_seriesid**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:72
msgid ""
"A multi-value variable containing the series MBIDs associated with the "
