"uitgavegroep zijn gekoppeld. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:74
msgid "**_releasegroup_seriescomment**"
msgstr "**_releasegroup_seriescomment**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:76
msgid ""
"A multi-value variable containing the series disambiguation comments "
"associated with the release group. (*since Picard 2.9*)"
msgstr ""
"Een meervoudige variabele met de verduidelijkingen van de series die aan de "
"uitgavegroep zijn gekoppeld. (*Sinds Picard 2.9.*)"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:78
msgid "**_releasegroup_seriesnumber**"
msgstr "**_releasegroup_seriesnumber**"

#: ../../variables/variables_advanced.rst:80
msgid ""
"If the release group is part of one of more series, this multi-value "
"variable contains the positions (numbers) of the release group in those "
